  "2026-04-06T17:13:16.366Z",codex-agent,"Progress: audited mutation-triggered cache invalidation wiring across CLI commands and hardened run-tracking paths. pm test now refreshes search artifacts when --run executes (to cover test_result_tracking item mutations) and pm test-all now refreshes using all touched item IDs after run aggregation."
  "2026-04-06T17:13:17.527Z",codex-agent,"Health policy remains compatibility-safe: pm health default behavior continues to refresh stale vectors unless disabled via --check-only or --no-refresh. Added release-readiness static guard to keep test run-tracking refresh wiring from regressing."
  "2026-04-06T17:13:19.140Z",codex-agent,"Verification evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts tests/unit/test-all-command.spec.ts tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts passed (83 tests)."
  "2026-04-06T18:47:06.630Z",codex-agent,"Hardened mutation-triggered search refresh coverage by ensuring test run-tracking and test-all mutation paths invalidate caches with touched item IDs while preserving default health stale-targeted refresh behavior. Added regression coverage and docs sync notes. Verification: pnpm build; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage."
